<html>
 <head>
  <title></title>
 </head>
 <body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 10px;" width="100%">
   <tbody>
    <tr>
     <td align="center" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
      <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff; width: 600px;">
       <tbody>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff;"><img alt="AN-email-header" src="{[devName:ANemailheader]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="AN-email-header" /><a href="https://www.alliancenursing.com.au"> </a></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="height: 30px;">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td align="left" style="padding: 0 45px;"><h1 style="font-size: 30px; line-height: 37px; color: #007DC3; font-weight: 900; font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Arial Black', Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</h1> <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},<br /> <br /> We’re sorry to hear you’ve had trouble accessing the Alliance Connect App. While we’re upgrading our technology, making sure you’re supported remains our top priority.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Here’s how to get up and running again:</p>
          <ol>
           <li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">First, delete and reinstall the app from the&nbsp;<a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6740983577">App Store</a> ​​​​​​or&nbsp;<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=au.com.allianceaustralia.connect">Google Play</a>&nbsp;.</li>
           <li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Check your inbox for an email titled "<em>Your new Alliance Connect password</em>". We've sent you a reset password link.</li>
           <li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Follow the link in that email to update your password and log in.</li>
          </ol> <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">Still having trouble or prefer to chat with someone? Give us a&nbsp;call&nbsp;on&nbsp;<a href="tel:1300034494">1300 034 494</a>, we're always happy to help!&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Kind regards,&nbsp;<br /> {{{Sender.FirstName}}}<br /> Alliance Nursing</p></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="height: 20px;">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 35px 0px 10px 0px;"><img alt="Alliance-graphic-line" src="{[devName:Alliancegraphicline]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="Alliance-graphic-line" /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 26px 45px 40px 45px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 22px;color: #374250;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="/* margin: 0 auto; */">
           <tbody>
            <tr>
             <td style="padding-right: 16px;"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/alliancenursingaustralia"><img alt="fb-blue" src="{[devName:fbblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="fb-blue" /></a></td>
             <td style="padding-right: 16px;"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/alliance-nursing-australia"><img alt="in-blue" src="{[devName:inblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="in-blue" /></a></td>
             <td style="padding-right: 16px;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/alliancenursingaustralia/"><img alt="is-blue" src="{[devName:isblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="is-blue" /></a></td>
             <td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnMTM3MLQMFYj52ERo0E00Q"><img alt="yt-blue" src="{[devName:ytblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="yt-blue" /></a></td>
            </tr>
           </tbody>
          </table></td>
        </tr>
       </tbody>
      </table></td>
    </tr>
   </tbody>
  </table>
 </body>
</html>